data.description: Welcome to New Tucson! Charming 2 Bedroom 2 Bath home that is on over an Acre. Tiled throughout entire Home so no carpet at all. Living room with French doors that open up to a covered porch. Wood burning fireplace in corner of Living room. Separate dining area just off kitchen or use it as the Home office. Large circular driveway and plenty of room to add onto the house, put up a large garage/workshop or put up a guest house. The possibilities are there for you to make it happen.
